    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine runs and the car is drivable, but you should expect some cosmetic wear on the interior and exterior, including minor dents and upholstery fading. There are a few minor mechanical items that will eventually need attention, such as aging suspension components and a slow leak in the power steering fluid. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind a bit of character and potential DIY maintenance.",
