    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of performance and value with this impeccably maintained vehicle. Presented in impressive condition, this model features a documented service history and has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure peak reliability. The exterior maintains a sharp, professional aesthetic, while the interior provides a clean and comfortable cabin for any journey. This is a premier opportunity for a driver seeking a high-quality, dependable vehicle that delivers exceptional long-term value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
